YDBOcto#1119 : INSERT via JDBC prepared statement using setTimestamp() and setBoolean()
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Before the fix this INSERT aborted with ERR_UNKNOWN_KEYWORD_STATE and closed the connection
(the JDBC driver reported SQLSTATE 08006 then 08003), so no rows were inserted. The driver
sends parameter type OID 0 (unspecified) for setTimestamp() and OID 16 (bool) for setBoolean(),
neither of which Octo resolved. After the fix the rows insert and read back correctly.

Table  : create table tii12 (id integer primary key, name varchar(20), ts timestamp, flag boolean)
Insert : insert into tii12 (id, name, ts, flag) values (?, ?, ?, ?)

Binding : id=1, name='alice', setTimestamp('2026-06-01 13:00:00'), setBoolean(true)
  --> INSERT 1 row
Binding : id=2, name='bob', setTimestamp('2024-12-31 12:00:00'), setBoolean(false)
  --> INSERT 1 row

Reading back : select id, name, ts, flag from tii12 order by id
1|alice|2026-06-01 13:00:00|t
2|bob|2024-12-31 12:00:00|f

Probing other JDBC setter / data-type combinations (each in its own connection):
  setLong       -> INTEGER     OK     : INSERT 1, read back 42
  setShort      -> INTEGER     OK     : INSERT 1, read back 7
  setByte       -> INTEGER     OK     : INSERT 1, read back 5
  setTime       -> TIME        OK     : INSERT 1, read back 13:45:00
  setTimestamp(.frac) -> TIMESTAMP OK     : INSERT 1, read back 2026-06-02 13:45:30.123
  setString(unspec) -> INTEGER OK     : INSERT 1, read back 42
  setString(unspec) -> NUMERIC OK     : INSERT 1, read back 3.14
  setString(unspec) -> BOOLEAN OK     : INSERT 1, read back t
  setString(unspec) -> DATE    OK     : INSERT 1, read back 2026-06-02
  setString(unspec) -> TIMESTAMP OK     : INSERT 1, read back 2026-06-02 13:45:30

Unresolvable unspecified-type parameters (clean error expected; connection must survive):
  INSERT..SELECT setTimestamp()    clean error : 42804 ERROR: Column "val" is of type TIMESTAMP but expression is of type PARAMETER
  INSERT..SELECT setTimestamp()    still alive : select 1 -> 1
  SELECT ? UNION SELECT 1 (unspec) clean error : 42601 ERROR: UNION types PARAMETER and INTEGER cannot be matched
  SELECT ? UNION SELECT 1 (unspec) still alive : select 1 -> 1
